description:
- The panel is by default hidden, appears when hovering the cursor in the left edge of working area within 1 second;
- Ads on the left panel removed;
- Resize top panel, changes image sizes and hover style on top panel elements (underline changes to blue flashing).

css:
@-moz-document domain("jsfiddle.net") {
#sidebar{
border-right: 3px solid white;
transition:left 100ms;
left:-190px!important;  
top:31px;
height:130%!important;
z-index:99999999999999;
}

#sidebar:hover{
transition:left 300ms;
transition-delay: 1s;
left:0px!important;
z-index:99999999999999;
}

#roadmap{
    display:none!important;
}
#s-bottom{
    display:none!important;
}

#result>.windowLabel{
  display: none !important;
}


#content{
margin-left: -8px;
left: 10px;
}

#actions{
top: -12px !important;
}

#progressbar{
top: 27px !important;
}

#header{
    height:30px !important;
}

#branding{
  display: none !important;
}

#usermenu img{
  width: 24px  !important;
    transform: scaleY(.70);
     margin-left:14px !important;
}

#actions .actionItem a.aiButton:hover {
    border-bottom: solid 0px #1C90F3  !important;
    color: #1C90F3 !important;
}
}
